        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow border-2 border-primary">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Business</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Per crescere con automazioni</p>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">‚Ç¨20/mese</div>
